American Presidents









Teaching elementary students about past American presidents doesn’t have to be boring. Our educational songs and videos about American presidents work as great activating strategies to get your elementary students engaged in learning. Our songs and videos are designed to be catchy and fun so your students stay interested throughout your lessons! We also offer worksheets and powerpoints to help support your lesson plans.


